Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:30.79,Default,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Božská technika!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.97,0:10:31.82,Default,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Božská technika!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.10,0:10:32.83,Default,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Božská technika!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:33.87,Default,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Božská technika!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:34.63,Default,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Božská technika!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:35.79,Default,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Božská technika!!
